293
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,440
Yuan Wuhuo.

294
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,200
Yuan Xizai.

295
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,600
Paano kawili-wili.

296
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:51,280
Paano mo nalaman
saan nakatago ang Star Stone?

297
00:22:52,360 --> 00:22:54,560
Mayroon bang ibang mga espiya
kabilang sa angkan ng Green Ape?

298
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:56,600
Mag-ulat!

299
00:22:57,360 --> 00:22:59,600
Master Wu Zhiqi,
Dumating na si Master Six-Eyed Butterfly.

300
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:01,840
- Nandito siya para kunin ang Star Stone.
- Sige.

301
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,800
Ang hawla na ito, tulad ng mga tanikala sa Tian Di,

302
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:09,880
